<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>182</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tuhin athak hehpihna gam nuomah,
 I Lalpau mun lopi;
 Kipahna pakcha hawih a lun ziechun,
 Tuoini nei ta puona.

[V2]
 Kipak in dan leh kikhawm hitiu.
 Vana Angel vam guol haw cheng tawh;
 Lungkhamna gama dahna cheng hih,
 I Lalpau ang a kipahna ding.

[V3]
 2. Ka damlai ni hi a tum ma sangsieh,
 Kei di'n meipi a zing
 Dantak leh zie gam chu ka tun tieng leh
 Sietlei hi ngai puong ie.

[V4]
 3. Tichun khawpi nuom lam chu zuon zelin,
 Sietlei ka gamlat zel
 Tuhin a pak gimlim ka tep pantai,
 Aw a nuom na ding e.

[V5]
 4. Ei hukdampa mel deih um tuoi nung khan,
 A Lalchutphah chungah;
 Vaihawm ina tatsate kipah nan,
 Hallelujah Amen.</lyrics>
<title>A Pak Gim Lim</title>
</song>